Thanks for your feedback!

@jonatack: I see your point and and agree that this is counter-productive w.r.t. to the planned fee rate improvements. Will take a deeper look at #20391 soon (put it into my evergrowing TOREVIEW file ;-)). 

 @practicalswift: As this PR would only change the usage in `ToString()` methods (i.e. for creating debug strings) it is not critical, but good hint anyway.
